---
layout: base
title: Portfolio
description: Explore Mert Biricik's portfolio of full stack development, data science, and system engineering projects, including demos and data visualizations.
priority: 0.9
changefreq: monthly
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-container">
    <h1 class="section-title">My Portfolio</h1>
    <p class="section-subtitle">A showcase of my work in full stack development, data science, and system engineering, including demos and data visualizations.</p>

    <div class="projects-grid">
      {%- for project in projects.all | reverse -%}
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-header">
          <h3 class="project-title">{{ project.title }}</h3>
          {% if project.subtitle %}
          <p class="project-subtitle">{{ project.subtitle }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="project-content">
          <p class="project-description">
            {{ project.overview }}
          </p>
          {% if project.tech and project.tech.length > 0 %}
          <div class="project-tech">
            {%- for tag in project.tech -%}
              <span class="tech-tag">{{ tag }}</span>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="project-links">
            {# <a href="/projects/{{ project.id }}/" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> View Details</a> #}
            {% if project.sourceLink %}
              <a href="{{ project.sourceLink }}" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> View Code</a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>

    <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
      <h2>Interested in Collaboration?</h2>
      <p>I'm always looking for exciting projects and opportunities to work with innovative teams. Let's discuss how we can work together.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">
          <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
          Get In Touch
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mertbiricik" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
          View GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>